fields.label: Google Calendar ID
fields.name: syn_new_calendar_id
fields.instructions: Value can be found in the calendar settings at Google Calendars.

fields.label: Host
fields.name: syn_video_host
fields.instructions: This widget works with YouTube and Vimeo hosted videos.

fields.label: Video ID
fields.name: syn_video_youtube_id
fields.instructions: Enter the YouTube Video ID which is a string of characters in the URL of the video hosted on YouTube.  For example, the Video ID of the video at https://youtube.com/XX11YY22ZZ33 is XX11YY22ZZ33.

fields.label: Playlist ID
fields.name: syn_video_youtube_playlist_id
fields.instructions: Enter the YouTube Playlist ID which is a string of characters in the URL of the playlist hosted on YouTube.  For example, the Playlist ID of the playlist at https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=XX11YY22XX11YY22 is XX11YY22XX11YY22.

fields.label: Video ID
fields.name: syn_video_vimeo_id
fields.instructions: Enter the Vimeo Video ID which is a string of characters in the URL of the video hosted on Vimeo.  For example, the Video ID of the video at https://vimeo.com/555555555 is 555555555.
